            "id": 6404002,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 南亞(1303)大漲7.04%，報79.1元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)01日10:20股價上漲5.2元，報79.1元，漲幅7.04%，成交52,324張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南亞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)所屬產業為塑膠工業，主要業務為各種塑膠加工品、塑膠原料、電子材料、聚酯纖維之製銷。及染整加工 、配電盤。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.21%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.73%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+849 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,713 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-4,571 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+3,707 張</li> <li>融資增減：-3,981 張</li> <li>融券增減：+328 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
